data.name: Tuna and Rice Bowl
data.quickTastyDescription: A light and refreshing bowl combining tender tuna with fluffy rice and vibrant vegetables, topped with a hint of spice.
detailedCookingInstructions: Prepare the white rice according to package instructions and set aside.
In a bowl, mix the drained tuna with soy sauce and sesame oil.
In a serving bowl, layer the cooked rice as the base.
Top with the seasoned tuna, diced cucumber, shredded carrot, and chopped green onion.
Drizzle sriracha sauce on top according to your spice preference.
Sprinkle sesame seeds to finish and enjoy!
data.detailedName: Tuna and Rice Bowl with Fresh Vegetables
